# modules/core/
#
# First-party module bundles ship here. Each module is a directory:
#
#   modules/core/<module-id>/
#   ├── manifest.yml              # validates against modules/catalogs/schemas/module.schema.json
#   ├── content/                  # HTML / PDF / Blockly / Python / WebXR assets
#   │   ├── en/
#   │   └── hi/
#   └── tests/                    # smoke tests for this module
#
# A reference task that adds a module: tasks/examples/SMO-9001-add-module-manifest.yml
